{"tid":1185312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反引渡修例走向世界　全球16個城市6月9日都示威","createTime":"2019-06-04T07:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T15:34:19.000Z","uid":47714,"like":85,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"155b2f448bb6a2fd36135e9705dec1cfbcf6cd01","tid":1185312,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:58:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://harbourtimes.com/2019/06/02/protest-vs-extradition-law-goes-global/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fharbourtimes.com%2F2019%2F06%2F02%2Fprotest-vs-extradition-law-goes-global%2F&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgjbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=7e775c6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://harbourtimes.com/2019/06/02/protest-vs-extradition-law-goes-global/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190602/59668441\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190602%2F59668441&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgjbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=09c134e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190602%2F59668441&h=a9d37666\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190602/59668441</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://harbourtimes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_20190602_1233491-e1559490904428.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fharbourtimes.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2FIMG_20190602_1233491-e1559490904428.jpg&h=58d2401e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1989年起移民外國的港加聯召集人馮玉蘭，以及移居美國已16年的「洛杉磯香港論壇」成員林先生，近日特別返港「撐香港」，呼籲港人6月9日上街「反送中」。 <br />\n<br />\n全球多個國家包括加拿大、美國、澳洲、英國和德國等多個城巿（包括多倫多、溫哥華、卡加利、紐約、洛杉磯、三藩巿、華盛頓、芝加哥、墨爾本、悉尼、里斯本、倫敦、柏林）的市民團體，已表明6月9日在當地發起「全球反送中遊行集會」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全球16城市反送中遊行集會詳情<br />\n<br />\n1）美國紐約市<br />\n時間：下午二時（東岸時區）<br />\n遊行起點：紐約時代廣場<br />\n遊行終點：中國駐紐約領事館<br />\n主辦團體：NY4HK - New Yorkers Supporting Hong Kong<br />\nNew York City, New York, USA<br />\nDate: 9th June, 2019<br />\nTime: 2pm EDT<br />\nStaring Location: Time Square (The right side of the large stairs)<br />\nEnding Location: Chinese Consulate, New York<br />\nOrganizer: NY4HK<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/326237484695680/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F326237484695680%2F&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgjbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=65611659\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/326237484695680/</a><br />\n===================================<br />\n2）美國三藩市<br />\n日期：二零一九年六月九號<br />\n時間：下午三時（太平洋時區）<br />\n遊行起點：三藩市唐人街花園角<br />\n遊行終點：香港駐三藩市經貿辦<br />\n主辦團體：北加香港會 N. Calif Hong Kong Club - 北加州香港會<br />\nSan Francisco, California<br />\nDate: 9th June, 2019<br />\nTime: 3:00pm (PDT)<br />\nStarting Location: Portsmouth Square<br />\nEnding Location: HKETO<br />\nOrganizer: Northern California Hong Kong Club<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/2471640139525017/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F2471640139525017%2F&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgjbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=5ec6c365\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/2471640139525017/</a><br />\n===================================<br />\n3）美國洛杉磯<br />\n日期：二零一九年六月九號<br />\n時間：下午二時 （太平洋時區）<br />\n活動地點：Grand Park<br />\n主辦團體：洛杉磯香港論壇 洛杉磯香港論壇 Hong Kong Forum, Los Angeles - Public<br />\nLos Angeles, California<br />\nDate: 9th June, 2019<br />\nTime: 2pm (PDT)<br />\nStarting Location: Grand Park, Los Angeles<br />\nOrganizer: Los Angeles Hong Kong Forum<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/677391609365623/?ti=icl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F677391609365623%2F%3Fti%3Dicl&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgjbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=19bab297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/677391609365623/?ti=icl</a><br />\n=======